name: Mvureni Fishermen Restaurant
description: MVURENI Fishermen Restaurant is a local community income generating project. The restaurant specializes in seafood. The fishermen sell their catch directly here. You find us direct on the Galu Beach just before Neptune hotels.  We offer Fresh seafood, cold drinks,Sun beds and WiFi free for customer. The atmosphere is one of he best in Diani Beach. The chefs, are some of the best with many years Experience in grill. We are looking forward to serving you a delicious mean right at the sandy beach.

name: Estuary Beach Lounge
description: Our Kitesurfing school and restaurant is a beautiful and familiar environment where you can find a special connection with the yourself and the others thanks to the amazing Baobabs and the unique Sundown in Diani Beach.

name: Sunnyside Up
description: Wholesome, fresh, continental comfort food, served in a beautiful beach front setting

name: Diana's Diani Bistro & Grill
description: DD's is a small, rustic & friendly owner-run establishment, situated in the heart of Diani. We offer good value, home cooked fresh dishes, such as pies, steaks, seafood, and wonderful vegetarian options; using locally sourced products.

name: Havana Bar
description: Chilled bar and restaurant with food from early til late. Great pizzas, seafood, snacks. Cocktails, cold beers all day long.

name: Blue Marlin Beach Restaurant
description: Beach Restaurant and Bar. Blue Marlin Beach Restaurant is known for its freshest seafood and breathtaking views of the Indian Ocean

name: Casamia
description: Italian Restaurant Lounge Bar. The home of Italian happy hour. Located along Diani Beach Road, our restaurant offers fine dining and exclusive lounging.
